theme is also style

in manifest file AndroidManifest.xml

<application
        android:allowBackup="true"
        android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher"
        android:label="@string/app_name"
        android:theme="@style/AppTheme">
        ...
    </application>

Theme attributes have a larger scope

colorPrimary
colorPrimaryDark
colorAccent
